# Sparkle Ed25519 signing material. Real keys live at
# ~/.config/sparkle/ outside the repo; the patterns below are
# defence-in-depth in case someone misconfigures `QM_SPARKLE_KEY`
# or accidentally copies a key into the repo root.
*.ed25519
*-ed25519.key
*-ed25519.pub
sparkle-private*.key
